flowchart TD
    %% PERF-TEST-AGENT orchestration flow from src/pipeline.py

    Start([Pipeline Trigger])
    Start --> Entry{Entry Mode}

    Entry -->|New Run| InitRun[initialize_run\n- create run_id\n- set current_phase\n- set PROMPT_REVIEW]
    Entry -->|Resume| LoadState[load_state + resume\nfrom saved pipeline_state.json]

    InitRun --> ExecLoop
    LoadState --> ExecLoop

    subgraph PhaseLoop[Phase Execution Loop (_execute_phases)]
        direction TD

        ExecLoop[Iterate PHASE_ORDER\n1 story_analysis\n2 test_planning\n3 env_triage\n4 script_data\n5 execution\n6 reporting\n7 postmortem]
        SkipDone{Phase already COMPLETED?}
        SetCurrent[Set current_phase]
        RunAgent[agent.run(state)]
        SaveState1[_save_state(state)]
        Failed{Phase status == FAILED?}
        HitlOn{HITL enabled?}
        HitlGate[_hitl_gate\n(UI callback or auto-approve)]
        Approved{Approved?}
        MarkComplete[Set COMPLETED\nstore approval notes\n_save_state]
        MarkRejected[Set REJECTED\nstore notes\n_save_state]
        StopAfter{stop_after reached?}

        ExecLoop --> SkipDone
        SkipDone -->|Yes| StopAfter
        SkipDone -->|No| SetCurrent --> RunAgent --> SaveState1 --> Failed

        Failed -->|Yes| EndFailed([End: Pipeline stopped on FAILED phase])
        Failed -->|No| HitlOn

        HitlOn -->|No| StopAfter
        HitlOn -->|Yes| HitlGate --> Approved

        Approved -->|Yes| MarkComplete --> StopAfter
        Approved -->|No| MarkRejected --> EndRejected([End: Pipeline stopped on REJECTED phase])

        StopAfter -->|Yes| EndStopped([End: Stopped after requested phase])
        StopAfter -->|No| NextPhase[Continue to next phase]
        NextPhase --> ExecLoop
    end

    EndFailed --> PersistFinal[Final _save_state]
    EndRejected --> PersistFinal
    EndStopped --> PersistFinal
    NextPhase -->|loop completes| PersistFinal

    PersistFinal --> Done([Pipeline Complete])

    subgraph InteractiveControls[Web UI / API Single-Phase Controls]
        direction TD
        PromptReview[mark_phase_for_modify\nstatus -> PROMPT_REVIEW]
        ExecuteOne[execute_phase\nPROMPT_REVIEW -> RUNNING -> RESULTS_READY]
        ApproveOne[approve_phase\napproved -> COMPLETED\nadvance -> next PROMPT_REVIEW]
    end

    PromptReview -. modifies current phase .-> ExecuteOne
    ExecuteOne -. result reviewed in UI .-> ApproveOne
    ApproveOne -. re-enters main phase order .-> ExecLoop
